data.description: Welcome to 916 Ludwig, nestled in a serene neighborhood. Admire the updated exterior boasting new siding, roof, gutters, and driveway (all revamped in 2022). Step inside to the luminous main level featuring a modern kitchen with granite countertops, newer dishwasher, and microwave, complemented by sleek LVP flooring extending into the dining area and upper level. Upstairs, revel in a spacious living room, renovated full bathroom, primary bedroom with a sizable walk-in closet, and a second bedroom. Descend to discover a cozy family room, two more bedrooms, and a renovated bathroom with a custom tiled shower. Ample storage and a workshop. Enjoy comfort with a new furnace, AC, and water heater. Step onto the patio to admire the new composite decking, metal railings, and concrete pad. The fenced backyard offers ample space. Nearby, indulge in 3 parks, walking trails, river proximity, easy access to 169, diverse shopping/dining, and schools. Move in and embrace the tranquility!
